READ‼️ I’ve been using the Himalaya Neem Face Wash 🌿 for a very long time. 
(Ps: I’m a combination skin, acne-prone girly 💁‍♀️) 
It did help control my acne, but things really changed when I discovered the Plum Salicylic Acid Foaming Face Wash 💧. After using both together, I saw a visible difference in my acne – like it reduced by 80% 😭✨ and I swear by this combo!

Here’s how I used it:
🌞 Morning – Only Himalaya Neem Face Wash
🌙 Night – First Himalaya, then Plum’s Salicylic Face Wash
🌆 Evening (if skin was dirty) – Used both
🌆 Evening (if skin was fine) – Just Plum’s Salicylic Face Wash

If you’re dealing with a lot of acne, you can use the salicylic acid face wash both times (after the neem one) and trust me, it works! 🙌

The Plum one also works as a great cleanser for acne-prone and oily skin. Do give it a try and I guarantee you’ll see the difference 💖
